Firstly the code gets by the parser. The parser checks the code''s syntax type errors line by line.
Secondly, after parsing, the JS engine breaks the codes into relevant pieces to interpret the codes effectively.
Then the codes are received by the interpreter who interpreted the codes into machine codes.
